snippet.title: By Moonlight Trailer (A Free Mystery / Relationship Visual Novel)
snippet.description:
Steam Store:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1014880/By_Moonlight/
Itch.io:  https://sugarhyped.itch.io/by-moonlight

Game is now out for download on Mac and Windows computers!

~ A Comedic Mystery Visual Novel with Relationship Building ~

Play as a paranormal investigator hired by the paranormal to investigate!

A series of events in which you search for a headless horseman's missing head before the night is over.

Features 5 different relationship routes, countless bad ends, and a variety of locations.

Can customize player name and pronouns~

Twitter @by_moonlight_vn
